title: [Warrior Guild, Entryway]
description: A long wall of native grey stone extends across a clearing, interrupted only by a wrought iron gate.  Two tall modwir trees stand guard a few paces in front of the entrance.

A long wall of native grey stone extends across a clearing, interrupted only by a wrought iron gate.  Two tall modwir trees stand guard a few paces in front of the entrance, their wide branches providing plentiful shade.  A grassy courtyard can be glimpsed through the wide bars of the gate.
